The authors of the open letter are confident that stricter legislation in the civil weapons sector will not be an inconvenience for the criminal to go to the black market.
Now, according to his words, in Moscow you can find any weapon at a low price.
Meanwhile, the Ministry of the Interior claims that the situation of the proliferation of illegal weapons is under control.
Suppliers: from factories to officers
The arms black market is supplied through various channels.
