The advertising company that made the video, BBH, hopes that with the ad they will be able to draw attention to the problem in a fun way.
Its creative director, Douglas Hamilton, says he wanted to use the power of music to get people to fulfill “their national duty.”
This is purely internet stuff, so we had to make it fun and funny.
This is the biggest problem in this country.
We’re the worst in the world at reproducing ourselves, so we felt this was an issue we had to address.
